solution: ```class Solution {
    public int addMinimum(String word) {
        int res = 0, expected = 0; // 0->'a', 1->'b', 2->'c'
        for (char c : word.toCharArray()) {
            int cur = c - 'a';
            res += (cur - expected + 3) % 3;
            expected = (cur + 1) % 3;
        }
        res += (3 - expected) % 3;
        return res;
    }
}
